h2. Welcome to RType

Rtype is a Ruby on Rails application that acts as a smart renderer for Movable Type blogs.
It sits on top of MT database, maps it to ActiveRecord and uses implements Rails conventions to bless MT with a proper MVC stack and improved performance.

h3. Usage

Keep on using MT's interface for the backend. Let Rtype do the rest.

h3. Features

* Automatic routing
* UltraSphinx powered search
* Fast, low "cost" comments
* Lightweight session management

h3. TODO

* Full integration with backend (templates, settings)
